        <h3>Konark Sun Temple</h3>
        <p>A UNESCO World Heritage Site, the 13th-century Sun Temple is known for its magnificent stone carvings.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Chilika Lake -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="slider">
          <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1d/Chilika_Lake_Odisha.jpg" class="slide active">
